				<li><a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/EN-US/LIBRARY/EE624351.ASPX" target="_blank">Microsoft Office 2013</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://products.office.com/en-ca/office-system-requirements#SUITES" target="_blank">Microsoft Office 2016</a></li>
			</ul>	
			</p>
			</div>
			
